<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Jmes Jems</h1>
    <p>
        Everything you find here has been hand-crafted by Jme herself. All items are unique and no two are the same.
        Every pet you see on Jmes Jems has been sent to Jme by the parents of the pets. If you would like your pet 
        drawn by Jme head on over to the contact page to find out where to send your favorite photo. All artwork is a 
        Jme origional, signed by Jme and personalized for you from Jme. So take a look around, you can find the links
        for site navigation to the left of the Home icon. Simply click on the Menu button and a dropdown will appear 
        with options under the Products heading. Jme is so excited that you have taken the time to stop by and enjoy 
        her work.
        She looks forward to creating for you.
